casional vs. pervasive) or any hidden data on Candidate\u202fA\u2019s stress tolerance, that could refine the assessment, but with the current evidence C remains the best candidate.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_3\", \"vote\": \"Candidate C\"}"}
